TextBlock.TextLine: Parisieñ ⁊ meldeñ ecclĩaꝵ collõnem ꝓvisionẽ p̃ntaciõem electiõem seu
quãvis aliã dispõem cõitꝰ vel divisim ꝑtineñ seu ꝑtinẽtib / si quod
vel si qua vacat seu vacant ad pñs vel cũ vacaverit aut cũ
simul vel successive vacav̾it qd̃ vel que ip̃e mag̃r Joħes
ꝑ se ṽl ꝓcur̃em suũ ad ħ legitimᵉ constitutũ dux̾it acceptandũ
vel acceptãda intimavit etc. liãs apᶜᵃˢ eidem mag̃ro Joħi
suꝑ huĩm grã cõcessi ⁊ cõfectis / Sub data Pisis noñ julii pontꝭ
etc. anno p̃mo . Necnon ꝓcessũ diaꝵ liaꝵ apᶜᵃʳ auc̃te ⁊ vigore ꝑ
venˡᵉᵐ. pr̃em dñm Abb̃em mõii sc̃e Genovefe Parisieñ executꝭ huĩm
gr̃e unacũ nõnullis aliis sint in ħ ꝑte collegꝭ cũ illa clã
qt̃s vos vel duo aut unꝰ vr̃um ꝑ vos vel aliũ seu alios etc.
apᶜᵃ auc̃te deputatũ / in debita forma cõfectũ.
Die qͥnta mẽsi decẽbĩ. Anno dñi m°. ccccᵐᵒ nono
Mag̃r baldoyunis de marla ⟦canᶜᵘˢ p̾beñ ecc̃e laudacieñ⟧ mag̃r
in artib ⁊ liceñ in legib canᶜᵘˢ. p̾beñ ecc̃e lauduneñ ꝓvidit
Bartholomeo Siram clic̃o diocꝭ xanctoneñ ⟦d⟧ ꝓtõri mag̃ri
guillĩ de marla liceñ in legꝭ ⁊ dñi nr̃i Regꝭ ꝯsiliarii de canᵗᵘ ⁊ preᵈᵃ
ecc̃e sc̃i med̾ici paꝵ quos dud̃ obtine̾ solebat deffꝭ mag̃r
Jo. de essoya ał ꝑ dc̃m ꝓcũrem acceptatꝭ / ut dicebat ⁊ petiit
instrũ. Pñtib Petro Wiart clĩco morineñ diocꝭ ⁊ Joħe
Bouteron clĩco Bituraceñ diocꝭ
Exposito dñis ꝑ magrũ matheũ garnerii ꝓcur̃em cõitatꝭ cappⁿᵒʳ ecc̃e
parisieñ ꝙ cũ deffũctus dñs Thomas boillardi quondã pb̃r ⁊
cappⁿᵘˢ. in ecc̃a parisieñ / in suo testaᵗᵒ seu ultĩa volũtate legaverit
cappⁿⁱˢ dc̃e cõitatꝭ sũmã xᶜᵉ̃ scutꝭ auri ꝓ una missa ꝑ ip̃os cappⁿᵒˢ ãnoq̃i
in dc̃a cõitate ꝑpetuo celeᵈᵃ. quãqͥdem sũmã conv̾ti voluit in empoiõem xᵉᵐ.
⟦xiiᵗᵉ̃⟧ solidi paꝵ Redditꝰ ãnui ⟦comu distribuend⟧. Supplicato ꝙ dñs
qt̃s dc̃is cappᵃⁿᵉ licenciã ꝯcede̾ vellent legatũ huim̃o acceptãdi
dñi licenciã huim̃oi eisd̃ cappⁿⁱˢ. cõcesserũt. Quiq̃dẽ ꝓcut̃or postea
dc̃am sũmã cõfessus fuit hãuisse ⁊ Realĩ Recepisse A Dño michaeli
boillardi executꝭ i testĩ dc̃i deffꝭ / qui dc̃am sũmã in mei p̃ncia
Tradidit Realĩ ⁊ assignavit clã vero testĩ dc̃i deffꝭ talis est
Itẽ ledit testateur laisse a la cõmunaulte de leglẽ de parꝭ pour acheter
x s. p̃. de Rente po̾ une messe lan ꝑpetuelmẽt pour le salut de son ame
pour ce xi l̃b. vis. t.
